Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)



10. GET /v2/entities/E, see D=zzz
=================================
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Length: 69
Content-Type: application/json
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)

{
    "D": {
